This is likely going to be painful for customers that are importing a space into an existing large instance (especially considering they can't do full site importers and need to import every space one-by-one).

This situation is complicated by the fact that AOD customer admins do not have a link to the content indexing page to trigger a full site index themselves (see [JST-4802|https://studio.atlassian.com/browse/JST-4802]). Although they are not blocked from going to the URL directly.

I propose we do the following:
- Provide a checkbox to let them choose whether to index or not.
- Fix [JST-4802|https://studio.atlassian.com/browse/JST-4802].
- Optionally: after a space is imported, provide a link to the content indexing page.

